515
00:46:50,850 --> 00:46:52,851
Idris, Owen, all of you,

516
00:46:52,935 --> 00:46:55,854
fetch everyone from
all the valleys 'round.

517
00:46:55,938 --> 00:46:57,606
Davy, over to
the other collieries.

518
00:46:57,690 --> 00:46:59,608
Invite everyone.
