547
00:49:20,249 --> 00:49:22,250
Good morning,
dear Mr. Gruffydd.
There is good to see you.

548
00:49:22,376 --> 00:49:23,585
Angharad is
at the market.

549
00:49:23,669 --> 00:49:26,004
Angharad?
Oh, I've come for Huw.

550
00:49:26,088 --> 00:49:27,172
For Huw?

551
00:49:28,883 --> 00:49:30,717
The daffodils
are out, Mama.

552
00:49:30,801 --> 00:49:31,885
Where are your
clothes, boy?

553
