554
00:49:33,054 --> 00:49:34,304
Your pillow?

555
00:49:34,388 --> 00:49:36,056
For these months,
ready for today.

556
00:49:36,140 --> 00:49:40,226
Come then, and you shall bring
back a posy fit for a queen

557
00:49:40,895 --> 00:49:42,979
for your brave mother.

558
00:49:43,064 --> 00:49:45,273
Indeed I will, sir.

559
00:49:52,573 --> 00:49:53,823
Almost there, Huw.

560
00:49:53,908 --> 00:49:55,492
Yes, sir.

561
00:49:55,576 --> 00:49:57,160
