Cwm Rhondda.

570
00:50:41,956 --> 00:50:43,373
But, Mr. Gruffydd...

571
00:50:46,001 --> 00:50:48,253
You can walk,
Huw, if you try.

572
00:50:50,506 --> 00:50:53,299
Come, lad.
You can walk.

573
00:50:57,054 --> 00:50:58,763
Huw! Walk!

574
00:51:07,398 --> 00:51:09,107
There's a good lad.

575
00:51:09,483 --> 00:51:10,942
Come on.

576
