a child into the world
against the Commandment!

611
00:55:07,846 --> 00:55:10,056
Prayer is wasted
on your sort!

612
00:55:10,599 --> 00:55:13,184
You shall be cast out
into the outer darkness

613
00:55:13,268 --> 00:55:15,186
till you have
learned your lesson!

614
00:55:16,355 --> 00:55:20,108
Ceinwen Lewis,
do you admit your sin?

615
00:55:27,199 --> 00:55:28,241
Yes.

616
00:55:30,577 --> 00:55:32,537
Then prepare to suffer
your punishment!

617
00:55:32,621 --> 00:55:33,621
Stop it!

618
00:55:33,706 --> 00:55:34,664
Angharad!

619
00:55:34,748 --> 00:55:36,207
Leave her alone,
you hypocrite!

620
00:55:36,291 --> 00:55:37,875
Sit down, Mr. Morgan.
You...

621
00:55:37,960 --> 00:55:39,252
Sit down!

622
00:55:39,336 --> 00:55:41,295
[Sobbing]

623
00:55:45,843 --> 00:55:47,719
How could you stand
there and watch them?

624
00:55:47,803 --> 00:55:50,805
Cruel old men
groaning and nodding
to hurt her more.

625
00:55:50,889 --> 00:55:52,724
That is not
the word of God.

626
00:55:52,808 --> 00:55:55,518
"Go thou,
and sin no more,"
Jesus said!

627
00:55:58,147 --> 00:55:59,439
Angharad!

628
00:56:10,826 --> 00:56:13,036
You know your Bible
too well, life too little.

629
00:56:13,120 --> 00:56:15,038
I know enough of life
to know that Ceinwen Lewis

630
00:56:15,122 --> 00:56:16,831
is no worse than I am.
Angharad!

631
00:56:16,915 --> 00:56:19,584
What do the deacons know?

632
00:56:19,668 --> 00:56:23,755
What do you know
about what could
happen to a poor girl

633
00:56:23,839 --> 00:56:25,089
when she loves
a man so much

634
00:56:25,174 --> 00:56:28,384
that to lose sight of him
for a moment is torture?

635
00:56:47,071 --> 00:56:48,321
Does that hurt you, Huw?

636
00:56:48,405 --> 00:56:49,906
Easy, now.

637
00:56:49,990 --> 00:56:51,074
Huw?

638
00:56:58,874 --> 00:57:01,250
Angharad. Angharad!

639
00:57:01,335 --> 00:57:03,669
I am a man now!
Kindly leave the kitchen!

640
00:57:03,796 --> 00:57:06,672
Oh, so you're
a man now, is it?

641
00:57:07,508 --> 00:57:08,508
Ow!

642
00:57:08,634 --> 00:57:10,676
Ha ha ha!

643
00:57:12,346 --> 00:57:13,971
Hey! Hey!

644
00:57:14,056 --> 00:57:16,766
Blasphemy, sacrilege,
and hypocrisy!

645
00:57:16,850 --> 00:57:19,268
Can't a man smoke
his pipe and read his
paper on the sabbath?

646
00:57:19,603 --> 00:57:21,771
Oh, go and
blow your nose!

647
00:57:23,857 --> 00:57:25,399
[Knock on Door]

