00:57:30,572 --> 00:57:35,034
[Knock Knock]

652
00:57:37,287 --> 00:57:39,122
What under the blaz...

653
00:57:39,206 --> 00:57:40,164
Good morning, Morgan.

654
00:57:40,249 --> 00:57:41,415
Good morning, Mr. Evans.

655
00:57:43,210 --> 00:57:45,169
Sit down, sir.
Sit down, sir.

656
00:57:45,254 --> 00:57:46,754
Oh. Thank you.

657
00:57:49,258 --> 00:57:50,716
Mr. Evans.

658
00:57:51,969 --> 00:57:53,886
The mine owner himself.

659
00:57:54,972 --> 00:57:56,222
Angharad.

660
00:58:00,519 --> 00:58:01,602
Ahh.

661
00:58:03,021 --> 00:58:04,814
Now to business, Morgan.

662
00:58:04,898 --> 00:58:06,149
Yes, sir.

663
00:58:07,192 --> 00:58:08,317
Uh...

664
00:58:10,195 --> 00:58:14,490
I've come here on a very
delicate mission, Morgan.

665
00:58:14,575 --> 00:58:15,825
No trouble, sir?

666
00:58:15,909 --> 00:58:20,496
No, no, no. No trouble,
but it worries me.

667
00:58:20,581 --> 00:58:21,914
Yes, sir.

668
00:58:22,791 --> 00:58:26,335
I'm here to get
your permission

669
00:58:27,921 --> 00:58:30,923
that my son lestyn

670
00:58:31,550 --> 00:58:33,217
may have permission...

671
00:58:33,302 --> 00:58:35,428
Ah-choo!

672
00:58:35,512 --> 00:58:36,512
Bless you, Morgan.

673
00:58:36,597 --> 00:58:37,597
Thank you, sir.

674
00:58:40,100 --> 00:58:41,893
Now, where was I?

675
00:58:41,977 --> 00:58:43,102
Permission.

676
00:58:43,437 --> 00:58:48,065
Oh, yes. That my son lestyn
may have permission,

677
00:58:48,150 --> 00:58:52,195
with your
daughter's permission,
to call upon her.

678
00:58:52,279 --> 00:58:53,362
There we are.

679
00:59:01,163 --> 00:59:04,248
We are a very proud
family, Mr. Evans.

680
00:59:04,333 --> 00:59:06,876
Yes, yes, I know,
I know, Morgan,

681
