00:59:16,136 --> 00:59:17,720
Thank you.
Thank you, Morgan.

686
00:59:17,804 --> 00:59:19,388
I'm very much
obliged to you.

687
00:59:19,473 --> 00:59:22,225
Yes, sir. Yes, sir.

688
00:59:22,309 --> 00:59:25,728
Good old Welsh blood,
you know, and all that
sort of thing.

689
00:59:25,812 --> 00:59:27,563
I'm very much
obliged, Morgan.

690
00:59:27,648 --> 00:59:29,065
Yes, sir. Yes, sir.

691
00:59:29,149 --> 00:59:30,483
Good day, Morgan.

692
00:59:30,567 --> 00:59:32,360
Beth! Beth!

693
00:59:32,653 --> 00:59:35,655
Come, come, come.
My shoes. Get my shoes.

694
00:59:35,739 --> 00:59:36,739
You, girl,
get up to your room.

695
00:59:36,823 --> 00:59:40,284
Have you no modesty
left in you? Get up there.

696
00:59:40,535 --> 00:59:43,829
