699
00:59:53,173 --> 00:59:55,091
Mr. Morgan.

700
00:59:55,175 --> 00:59:56,509
Sit down.

701
01:00:07,354 --> 01:00:09,522
This is my wife
Mrs. Morgan.

702
01:00:10,857 --> 01:00:12,358
How do you do?

703
01:00:14,152 --> 01:00:16,737
Mr. Morgan,
I've come to ask
your permission

704
01:00:16,822 --> 01:00:19,323
to speak to your
daughter Angharad.

705
01:00:30,877 --> 01:00:32,545
These are my sons.

706
01:00:33,922 --> 01:00:35,923
Yes. I know them.

707
01:00:42,973 --> 01:00:44,015
Ah-choo!

708
01:00:44,057 --> 01:00:46,058
God bless you.
God bless you.

709
01:01:27,559 --> 01:01:29,477
[Clock Strikes 9:00]

710
01:01:48,080 --> 01:01:50,039
You shouldn't be here.

711
01:01:50,123 --> 01:01:53,584
I couldn't spend another
night without knowing.

712
01:01:53,668 --> 01:01:56,337
What has happened?
Is anything wrong?

713
01:01:56,421 --> 01:01:57,838
Wrong?

714
01:01:57,923 --> 01:02:00,007
You know what I mean.

715
01:02:00,092 --> 01:02:02,218
Why have you
changed towards me?

716
01:02:02,302 --> 01:02:04,553
Why am I a stranger now?

717
01:02:04,638 --> 01:02:06,430
Have I done anything?

718
01:02:08,975 --> 01:02:10,309
No.

719
01:02:12,479 --> 01:02:14,313
The blame is mine.

720
01:02:15,982 --> 01:02:18,234
Your mother spoke
to me after chapel.

721
01:02:18,318 --> 01:02:22,071
She's happy to think
you'll be having
plenty all your days.

722
01:02:22,155 --> 01:02:23,614
Lestyn Evans.

723
01:02:26,952 --> 01:02:28,077
You could do no better.

724
01:02:28,161 --> 01:02:30,955
I don't want him!
I want you.

725
01:02:32,165 --> 01:02:33,416
Angharad.

726
01:02:39,589 --> 01:02:43,008
I have spent nights, too,
trying to think this out.

727
01:02:45,011 --> 01:02:48,472
When I took up this work,
I knew what it meant.

728
01:02:48,557 --> 01:02:51,809
It meant sacrifice
and devotion.

729
01:02:51,893 --> 01:02:54,437
It meant making
it my whole life

730
01:02:54,521 --> 01:02:58,232
to the...
To the exclusion
of everything else.

731
01:02:59,401 --> 01:03:01,902
That I was perfectly
willing to do.

732
01:03:04,948 --> 01:03:06,198
But to share it
with another...

733
01:03:08,201 --> 01:03:11,120
Do you think
I will have you going
threadbare all your life,

734
01:03:11,204 --> 01:03:14,081
depending on
the charity of others
for your good meals,

735
01:03:14,166 --> 01:03:16,959
our children growing up
in cast-off clothing,

736
01:03:17,043 --> 01:03:20,629
and ourselves
thanking God for parenthood
in a house full of bits?

737
01:03:20,881 --> 01:03:26,135
No. I can bear
with such a life for
the sake of my work,

738
01:03:26,219 --> 01:03:30,055
but I think
I'd start to kill

739
01:03:30,140 --> 01:03:34,977
if I saw the white
come to your hair
20 years before its time.

740
01:03:36,646 --> 01:03:38,063
Why?

741
01:03:41,818 --> 01:03:43,944
Why would you
start to kill?

742
01:03:44,905 --> 01:03:48,365
Are you a man
or a saint?

743
01:03:48,450 --> 01:03:50,075
I am no saint,

744
01:03:50,160 --> 01:03:52,286
but I have a duty
towards you.

745
01:03:52,370 --> 01:03:54,038
Let me do it.

746
01:04:51,763 --> 01:04:53,681
